=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 25, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xzo1665702759148.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xzo1665702759148.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xzo1665702759148.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xzo1665702759148\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Operation activated by the SAX parser for each namespace specification in a start tag,\n    when the parser encounters the corresponding end tag.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104xzo1665702759148_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"xzo1665702759148__codeblock_h3n_123_hwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation ENDPREFIXMAPPING\n  params\n     string Prefix: in\n  endparams\n\nImplement your code here\n\nend; ENDPREFIXMAPPING operation</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xzo1665702759148__section_bgz_c23_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d438863e53\">Parameters</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xzo1665702759148__p_d136886e1_d136887e1_d136888e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Prefix</var>—namespace identifier</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xzo1665702759148__section_drv_223_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d438863e64\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xzo1665702759148__p_d136892e1_d136893e1_d136894e1\">When this operation is defined, it is called by\n          <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">PARSE</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">PARSEFILE</span> when the end tag belonging to a\n        start tag that has an <code class=\"ph codeph\">xmlns</code> attribute is encountered. It is called once for\n        each <code class=\"ph codeph\">xmlns</code> specification in the start tag, in reverse order, and it is\n        called before the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">STARTELEMENT</span> operation.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xzo1665702759148__p_d136895e1_d136896e1_d136897e1\">For example, given the following XML code:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104xzo1665702759148_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"xzo1665702759148__codeblock_opf_l23_hwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">&lt;a:y xmlns=\"http://www.mywebsite.com/default\"\n     xmlns:a=\"http://www.mywebsite.com/a.html\"\n     xmlns:b=\"http://www.mywebsite.com/b.html\"&gt; ...\n&lt;/a:y&gt;</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xzo1665702759148__p_d136898e1_d136899e1_d136900e1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">ENDPREFIXMAPPING</span> is called for each\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">xmlns</code> specification, in the following order:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"xzo1665702759148__table_d16316e1_d16317e1_d16318e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Invocation Parameter Values</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xzo1665702759148__table_d16316e1_d16317e1_d16318e1__entry__1\">For XML</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xzo1665702759148__table_d16316e1_d16317e1_d16318e1__entry__2\">Value of Prefix</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xzo1665702759148__table_d16316e1_d16317e1_d16318e1__entry__3\">Comments</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xzo1665702759148__table_d16316e1_d16317e1_d16318e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">xmlns:a=\"http://www.mywebsite.com/b.html\"</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xzo1665702759148__table_d16316e1_d16317e1_d16318e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"b\"</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xzo1665702759148__table_d16316e1_d16317e1_d16318e1__entry__3\">Indicates the end of the scope of prefix\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">b</code>. Subsequent tags in the XML document cannot use this prefix,\n                without redefining it using a <code class=\"ph codeph\">xmlns:b=</code>  specification.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xzo1665702759148__table_d16316e1_d16317e1_d16318e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">xmlns:a=\"http://www.mywebsite.com/a.html\"</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xzo1665702759148__table_d16316e1_d16317e1_d16318e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"a\"</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xzo1665702759148__table_d16316e1_d16317e1_d16318e1__entry__3\">Indicates the end of the scope of prefix\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">a</code>. Subsequent tags in the XML document cannot use this prefix,\n                without redefining it using a <code class=\"ph codeph\">xmlns:a=</code>  specification.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xzo1665702759148__table_d16316e1_d16317e1_d16318e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">xmlns=\"http://www.mywebsite.com/default\"</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xzo1665702759148__table_d16316e1_d16317e1_d16318e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"\"</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xzo1665702759148__table_d16316e1_d16317e1_d16318e1__entry__3\">Indicates the end of the scope of the default\n                namespace. Subsequent tags without a prefix will not belong to this default\n                namespace.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kch1665703202145.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>PARSE</a><p>Parses a specified XML stream.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ttv1665703202809.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>PARSEFILE</a><p>Parses an XML document in the specified file.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rcp1665702759080.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>STARTPREFIXMAPPING</a><p>Operation activated by the SAX parser when it encounters a start tag with one or more xmlns (namespace) specifications.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vtr1665703208047.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>STARTELEMENT</a><p>Operation activated by the SAX parser when a start tag is encountered.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533994\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533994\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "ENDPREFIXMAPPING Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 25, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Operation activated by the SAX parser for each namespace specification in a start tag, when the parser encounters the corresponding end tag. Explain this code operation ENDPREFIXMAPPING params string Prefix: in endparams Implement your code here end; ENDPREFIXMAPPING operation Copy Parameters Prefix —namespace identifier Description When this operation is defined, it is called by PARSE and PARSEFILE when the end tag belonging to a start tag that has an xmlns attribute is encountered. It is called once for each xmlns specification in the start tag, in reverse order, and it is called before the STARTELEMENT operation. For example, given the following XML code: Explain this code <a:y xmlns=\"http://www.mywebsite.com/default\" xmlns:a=\"http://www.mywebsite.com/a.html\" xmlns:b=\"http://www.mywebsite.com/b.html\"> ... </a:y> Copy ENDPREFIXMAPPING is called for each xmlns specification, in the following order: Table 1. Invocation Parameter Values For XML Value of Prefix Comments xmlns:a=\"http://www.mywebsite.com/b.html\" \"b\" Indicates the end of the scope of prefix b . Subsequent tags in the XML document cannot use this prefix, without redefining it using a xmlns:b= specification. xmlns:a=\"http://www.mywebsite.com/a.html\" \"a\" Indicates the end of the scope of prefix a . Subsequent tags in the XML document cannot use this prefix, without redefining it using a xmlns:a= specification. xmlns=\"http://www.mywebsite.com/default\" \"\" Indicates the end of the scope of the default namespace. Subsequent tags without a prefix will not belong to this default namespace. Related Links PARSE Parses a specified XML stream. PARSEFILE Parses an XML document in the specified file. STARTPREFIXMAPPING Operation activated by the SAX parser when it encounters a start tag with one or more xmlns (namespace) specifications. STARTELEMENT Operation activated by the SAX parser when a start tag is encountered. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}